EN: This city has many beautiful gardens.

ZH: 我们可以在园林里散步。
EN: We can take a walk in the garden.

ZH: 这座园林的设计非常精致。
EN: The design of this garden is very exquisite.

ZH: 园林里的花朵都开得很漂亮。
EN: The flowers in the garden are all blooming beautifully.

ZH: 这个园林有一个漂亮的喷泉。
EN: This garden has a beautiful fountain.

ZH: 我们在园林里安排了一场野餐。
EN: We have arranged a picnic in the garden.

ZH: 园林里有很多树木和灌木。
EN: There are many trees and shrubs in the garden.

ZH: 这个园林是我小时候常去的地方。
EN: This garden is a place I used to go to often when I was a child.

ZH: 我们可以在园林里看到各种各样的鸟类。
EN: We can see a variety of birds in the garden.

ZH: 春天是园林最美丽的时候。
EN: Spring is the most beautiful time of the garden.

ZH: 园林里有一个小桥跨过小溪。
EN: There is a small bridge over a stream in the garden.

ZH: 园林里有一个大草坪，孩子们可以在那里玩耍。
EN: There is a big lawn in the garden where children can play.

