EN: This garden is one of the famous tourist attractions.

ZH: 园林里有一个小湖，可以划船。
EN: There is a small lake in the garden where you can row a boat.

ZH: 傍晚时分，园林里会点亮各种彩灯。
EN: In the evening, various colored lights will illuminate the garden.

